metadata.name: Angelica 1
metadata.description:
“She bares her soul bathed in light.” Angelica One is the first NFT in the collection [“Bare Implications”](https://foundation.app/collection/bare-implications). This NFT was created out of a collaboration between photographer Mark Johnson and model Angelica.

Owner of this NFT will be granted collector access to the platform [ModNFT.io](https://modnft.io) and be eligible to view exclusive content related to this NFT and collection as well as receive airdrops and other perks from the project.
